Package reading.kartik.ArtificialSimulator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnEntity
    This class consists of attributes and methods to define an Entity.
    AnInterface
    This is the class where all the GUI goodness happens, It draws, and moves the entities, when it is made to run.
    AWorld
    This is the class where most of the crucial under the hood scenes happen.
    Carnivore
    This class inherits from AnEntity, and is used to create objects of type Herbivores.
    Food
    This class extends AnEntity, and is used to create and store food objects in the world.
    Herbivore
    This classs extends AnEntity, and is used to create and store a food's parameters.
    Obstacle
    This class extends AnEntity, and is used to define and store an obstacle's parameters.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    This is an enum, used to create and return random direction values.
